<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #1E91B0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #1E91B0;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        th, td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #1E91B0;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Booking Confirmation</h1>
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for your booking! Below are the details of your order:</p>
        
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Name</th>
                <th>Email</th>
                <th>Phone</th>
                <th>Quantity</th>
                <th>Booking Date</th>
                <th>Total Price</th>
                <th>Product Name</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>{{name}}</td>
                <td>{{email}}</td>
                <td>{{telepon}}</td>
                <td>{{quantity}}</td>
                <td>{{dateAt}}</td>
                <td>{{totalPrice}}</td>
                <td>{{productName}}</td>
            </tr>
            <!-- Repeat the above row for each product in the order -->
        </table>

        <p>Thank you for choosing our service. We look forward to serving you!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
